high_descs: Turn around and then go left to the stove.
Pick up the pot from the back right burner of the stove.
Carry the pot and turn around to find the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the pot inside, shut the door. Open the door and take the pot out then shut the door.
Hold the pot and turn around then to the left to find the toaster.
Place the pot on the counter, to the left of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Chill a pot and place it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around, go forward, turn right, go forward, turn left and go to the stove
Pick up the pot on the stove
Turn around, go to the fridge
Put the pot in the fridge, wait, pick up the pot
Turn around, go forward a bit, turn right, go to the counter
Put the pot near the toaster
anns.task_desc: Cool a pot and bring it to the counter

high_descs: Turn around, hang a left at the door, turn right just past the fridge and walk to the white stove ahead.
Pick up the gold pot from the back right corner of the stove.
Turn around and walk to the fridge ahead across the room.
Put the pot inside the fridge on the middle shelf to the left of the tomato, chill it for seven seconds, remove it and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the counter with the toaster ahead.
Put the chilled pot on the counter to the right of the head of lettuce on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled pot on a counter.
